{"id": "anc_breadcrumb_grow", "modality": "animations", "name": "Breadcrumb Grow", "task": {"description": "Create a self-contained 1920x1080 HTML animation (inline CSS, NO <canvas>) of a breadcrumb trail building up. Starting from 'Home', segments append one-by-one over ~3.5s ('Home > Library > Datasets > Vision > train-2026') with a chevron separator between each. The trail stays on one left-aligned horizontal line and must not run off the right edge (it stays within a max-width container).", "requirements": ["Breadcrumb segments append over time (more segments visible in later frames)", "All segments and chevrons stay on one horizontal line (aligned, same vertical center) at every frame", "The trail never runs off the right edge of the viewport (it stays within bounds, e.g. ellipsizing or wrapping inside its container)", "By the final frame all five segments are present in order with chevron separators", "Segments and chevrons do not overlap each other", "No horizontal scrollbar appears at any frame"], "difficulty": "hard"}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 13, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 2034, "rv_n_defects": 8, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 9818}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 5, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 2333, "rv_n_defects": 5, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 10286}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 5, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 2272, "rv_n_defects": 3, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 10603}], "ss_img": "images/animations/anc_breadcrumb_grow_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/animations/anc_breadcrumb_grow_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Breadcrumb Trail Animation</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: flex-start;\n            padding: 0 120px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .breadcrumb-container {\n            max-width: 1680px;\n            width: 100%;\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);\n            padding: 60px 80px;\n            border-radius: 24px;\n            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n        }\n\n        .breadcrumb-title {\n            font-size: 48px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: #2d3748;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .breadcrumb-trail {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            flex-wrap: nowrap;\n            gap: 0;\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: 500;\n            line-height: 1.2;\n        }\n\n        .breadcrumb-item {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            opacity: 0;\n            transform: translateX(-30px);\n            animation-fill-mode: forwards;\n        }\n\n        .breadcrumb-text {\n            color: #4a5568;\n            padding: 16px 24px;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.08);\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\n            white-space: nowrap;\n        }\n\n        .breadcrumb-text:hover {\n            background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.15);\n            color: #3730a3;\n        }\n\n        .breadcrumb-separator {\n            margin: 0 20px;\n            color: #a0aec0;\n            font-size: 28px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n        }\n\n        .breadcrumb-item:last-child .breadcrumb-text {\n            background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);\n            color: #3730a3;\n            font-weight: 600;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes slideInFade {\n            to {\n                opacity: 1;\n                transform: translateX(0);\n            }\n        }\n\n        .breadcrumb-item.animate {\n            animation: slideInFade 0.6s ease-out forwards;\n        }\n\n        .breadcrumb-item:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0s; }\n        .breadcrumb-item:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.7s; }\n        .breadcrumb-item:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 1.4s; }\n        .breadcrumb-item:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 2.1s; }\n        .breadcrumb-item:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 2.8s; }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n        <h1 class=\"breadcrumb-title\">Navigation Path</h1>\n        <nav class=\"breadcrumb-trail\" id=\"breadcrumbTrail\">\n            <!-- Items will be added dynamically -->\n        </nav>\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        const breadcrumbData = [\n            { text: 'Home', isLast: false },\n            { text: 'Library', isLast: false },\n            { text: 'Datasets', isLast: false },\n            { text: 'Vision', isLast: false },\n            { text: 'train-2026', isLast: true }\n        ];\n\n        const breadcrumbTrail = document.getElementById('breadcrumbTrail');\n        \n        function createBreadcrumbItem(data, index) {\n            const item = document.createElement('div');\n            item.className = 'breadcrumb-item';\n            \n            const text = document.createElement('span');\n            text.className = 'breadcrumb-text';\n            text.textContent = data.text;\n            \n            item.appendChild(text);\n            \n            if (!data.isLast) {\n                const separator = document.createElement('span');\n                separator.className = 'breadcrumb-separator';\n                separator.innerHTML = '&#8250;'; // Right-pointing angle quotation mark\n                item.appendChild(separator);\n            }\n            \n            return item;\n        }\n\n        function animateBreadcrumbs() {\n            breadcrumbData.forEach((data, index) => {\n                const item = createBreadcrumbItem(data, index);\n                breadcrumbTrail.appendChild(item);\n                \n                // Trigger animation after a short delay to ensure DOM is ready\n                setTimeout(() => {\n                    item.classList.add('animate');\n                }, 100);\n            });\n        }\n\n        // Start animation when page loads\n        window.addEventListener('load', () => {\n            setTimeout(animateBreadcrumbs, 200);\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>", "rv_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Breadcrumb Trail Animation</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: flex-start;\n            padding: 0 120px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .breadcrumb-container {\n            max-width: 1680px;\n            width: 100%;\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);\n            padding: 60px 80px;\n            border-radius: 24px;\n            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n        }\n\n        .breadcrumb-title {\n            font-size: 48px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: #2d3748;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .breadcrumb-trail {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            flex-wrap: nowrap;\n            gap: 20px;\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: 500;\n            line-height: 1.2;\n        }\n\n        .breadcrumb-item {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            opacity: 0;\n            transform: translateX(-30px);\n            animation-fill-mode: forwards;\n        }\n\n        .breadcrumb-text {\n            color: #4a5568;\n            padding: 16px 24px;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.08);\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\n            white-space: nowrap;\n            width: 200px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .breadcrumb-text:hover {\n            background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.15);\n            color: #3730a3;\n        }\n\n        .breadcrumb-separator {\n            color: #a0aec0;\n            font-size: 28px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            width: 40px;\n            text-align: center;\n            flex-shrink: 0;\n        }\n\n        .breadcrumb-item:last-child .breadcrumb-text {\n            background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);\n            color: #3730a3;\n            font-weight: 600;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes slideInFade {\n            to {\n                opacity: 1;\n                transform: translateX(0);\n            }\n        }\n\n        .breadcrumb-item.animate {\n            animation: slideInFade 0.6s ease-out forwards;\n        }\n\n        .breadcrumb-item:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0s; }\n        .breadcrumb-item:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.7s; }\n        .breadcrumb-item:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 1.4s; }\n        .breadcrumb-item:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 2.1s; }\n        .breadcrumb-item:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 2.8s; }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n        <h1 class=\"breadcrumb-title\">Navigation Path</h1>\n        <nav class=\"breadcrumb-trail\" id=\"breadcrumbTrail\">\n            <div class=\"breadcrumb-item\">\n                <span class=\"breadcrumb-text\">Home</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"breadcrumb-item\">\n                <span class=\"breadcrumb-separator\">\u203a</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"breadcrumb-item\">\n                <span class=\"breadcrumb-text\">Library</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"breadcrumb-item\">\n                <span class=\"breadcrumb-separator\">\u203a</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"breadcrumb-item\">\n                <span class=\"breadcrumb-text\">Datasets</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"breadcrumb-item\">\n                <span class=\"breadcrumb-separator\">\u203a</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"breadcrumb-item\">\n                <span class=\"breadcrumb-text\">Vision</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"breadcrumb-item\">\n                <span class=\"breadcrumb-separator\">\u203a</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"breadcrumb-item\">\n                <span class=\"breadcrumb-text\">train-2026</span>\n            </div>\n        </nav>\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {\n            const breadcrumbItems = document.querySelectorAll('.breadcrumb-item');\n            \n            // Start the animation sequence\n            setTimeout(() => {\n                breadcrumbItems.forEach(item => {\n                    item.classList.add('animate');\n                });\n            }, 300);\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>"}